{"word":"καταφαγεῖν","slug":"καταφαγεῖν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καταφαγεῖν</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>serving as aor2 to <a href='S:κατεσθίω'><el>κατεσθίω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to devour, eat up</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to spend in eating, waste, devour</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}